:: Public Holidays
"Nova godina"			public on january 1 length 2 days
"Doček Nove godine neradni dan"	public on ( ( ( [january 2] == [sunday after ([january 2])] ) ) ? [ monday after ([january 2]) ] : noop )
"Dan nezavisnosti"		public on march 1
"Praznik rada"			public on may 1 length 2 days
"Praznik rada neradni dan"	public on ( ( ( [may 2] == [sunday after ([may 2])] ) ) ? [ monday after ([may 2]) ] : noop )
"Dan državnosti"		public on november 25
"Božić (katolički)"		public on december 25

"Ramazanski bajram"		public religious on march 31 2025
"Kurbanski bajram"		public religious on june 6 2025
"Ramazanski bajram"		public religious on march 20 2026
"Kurbanski bajram"		public religious on may 27 2026

"Uskrs (katolički)"		public religious on easter
"Uskrsni ponedjeljak (katolički)" public religious on easter plus 1
